**Crazy Classroom**

a. Modeling
	- Classrooms Occupation
		* Maintainer (Name of Department / School / StudentSociety)
		* Time Span (Example Fri 1,2) --> Similiar as the way Calendar software does
		* Classroom ID
		* OccupationType (Class / Events) --> To be specific
		* Meta (Use json to save detail information such as classID/eventName)
		Todo:
			1.Refer Calendar software 's database;
			2.Make a detail list of occupation types.

	- Classrooms
		* ID (An unique integer) int
		* Room Name (101, 102) string
		* Campus (Liangxiang or Zhongguancun) --> Hard code the list
		* Capacity (Example: 100 people)
		* Room Facilities (Projector, Remote Microphone, Computer, 
							Video Recorder, Air-Conditioner, Fan, etc.)
		* BuildingID
		* Floor (Example: 2F) float

	- Areas: Make groups for classrooms (which may be used in room determining algorithm)
		* Temperature
		* Sunshine Time Span
			+ Solar Elevation Angle
			+ Height of the Obtruct outside
	- Building
		* Hours (Open/Close Time)
	
b. User Interfaces
	- Start search
	- Classrooms result list
	- Classroom detail
		* Current Status
		* Upcoming Events
		* Maintainer


c. Time Tables